stanford pre business association for gsb mentors for gsb mentors thank you for your interest in getting involved the stanford pre business association appreciates the contribution of your time to help create a stronger support system for stanford's future business men and women we welcome you to share your passion insights and experiences from the working world with our members for more information email spbamentorshipprogram gmail com here are a few of the ways you can help the stanford pre business assocation hosts bi weekly luncheons with speakers from the graudate school of business the luncheons are informal a conversation rather than a lecture where undergraduates are encouraged to ask questions and contribute to the conversation we also organize a mentorship program between the graduate school of business and undergraduate students matching participants with similar interests and maintaining a low mentee to mentor ratio apply to be a gsb mentor spba organizes one of the most popular mentorship programs on campus the program is a platform that connects undergraduates and gsb students and serves as a foundation for career and interest networks between them the program matches undergraduates with gsb students willing to act as mentors to the undergraduates and give them advice about business related careers and business school in order to ensure quality mentoring relationships we try our best to match participants with similar interests and to maintain a low mentee to mentor ratio we hold regular informal gatherings 1 2 per quarter and encourage individual meetings with your mentee throughout the year please download the following forms for the undergraduate and graduate applications undergraduate mentee application graduate mentor application join us send an email to prebusiness join lists stanford edu upcoming events january 10 2011 stanford apprentice application deadline location stanfordapprentice com time 11 59pm january 12 2011 consulting internships resume and interview workshop location by rsvp time 7pm 8pm
